<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1418,1443]" pageId="2" pageNumber="497">Distribution.</emphasis>
North Sea; Mediterranean Sea; 
<collectingCountry box="[712,770,1418,1443]" name="India" pageId="2" pageNumber="497">India</collectingCountry>
